{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_04_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある日の午後",
      "startTime": 0.2066666762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんはライブを中心に活動しているけど\nライブ以外の仕事はどう思っているんだ？",
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私はライブパフォーマンスでファンのみなさんに\n楽しんでもらうことがアイドルの本分だと思っています",
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、トリエルの知名度が上がるのなら\n苦手な仕事に挑戦することもやぶさかではありません",
      "startTime": 19,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でもこれはやりたくないという線引きはあるのか？",
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "明確な線引きはありません。今までしたことがなかった\n水着グラビアも星見プロに来て解禁しましたし……",
      "startTime": 30.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時は苦労を掛けてすまなかった",
      "startTime": 35.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい\n{user}さんのことは信頼していますから",
      "startTime": 40.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが取ってきた仕事なら\n間違いはないと信じています",
      "startTime": 45.5645600924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえるのは嬉しいが、責任重大だな……\n実は天動さんに新しい仕事のオファーがきてるんだ",
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "それは私の苦手な仕事ということですか？",
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "苦手かどうかは分からないが、かなり大変な仕事だ\nただ、俺はこの仕事は天動さんに似合っていると思う",
      "startTime": 66.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんは毎年横浜で行われている\n若い女性向けのファッションショーを知ってるか？",
      "startTime": 73.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、毎年数万人の観客を集める国内最大規模の……\nもしかして、そのショーに私が出るんですか？",
      "startTime": 82.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。天動さんにファッションモデルとして\n出演してほしいというオファーが来たんだよ",
      "startTime": 89.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "国内のトップモデルが大勢出演する大イベントだ\nモデル未経験の天動さんには荷が重いかもしれないが",
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。でもこれはチャンスです\n私の出演はトリエルのいいプロモーションになります",
      "startTime": 104.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ファッションモデルは未知の体験なので\nうまくやれるか分かりませんが……",
      "startTime": 111.3938782505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "やるからには全力を尽くします。アイドルだから\n下手でも仕方ないなんて、絶対に言わせません",
      "startTime": 117.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEの……いえ、星見プロの\n代表として立派にモデルを務めてみせます！",
      "startTime": 125.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺も出来る限りサポートするつもりだ\n大変だと思うが頑張って成功させよう",
      "startTime": 131.6766893228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頼りにしています、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 134.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、今日からモデルのトレーニングを\n始めることになったんだが……",
      "startTime": 143.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ただでさえ毎日ハードなダンスレッスンをしているのに\nさらにモデルの練習までするのは大変じゃないか？",
      "startTime": 150.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "ですがアイドルとして歌とダンスのレッスンを\n削る訳にはいきません",
      "startTime": 157.3487557965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "それに体力の限界までトレーニングすることには\n慣れています。心配はいりません",
      "startTime": 162.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "体力の限界までやることに\n慣れちゃいけないと思うが……",
      "startTime": 167.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "ファッションショーに出ることを優とすみれに話したら\n二人とも凄く喜んで応援してくれました",
      "startTime": 173.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "二人の期待を裏切らないためにも\nどんなに過酷な練習メニューでもやり遂げてみせます！",
      "startTime": 179.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "意気込みは分かったが無理はしないようにな\nそれで、今日はどんなトレーニングをするつもりだ？",
      "startTime": 186.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "モデルで大切なのは美しいウォーキングです\nそこで優があれを用意してくれました",
      "startTime": 193.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……ハイヒールと大量の本？",
      "startTime": 196.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "モデルと言えばかかとの高い靴は欠かせません\nハイヒールで颯爽と歩く姿は格好いいですよね",
      "startTime": 203.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "私もそんな格好いいウォーキングに憧れますが……\n私は普段かかとの高い靴をあまり履かないんです",
      "startTime": 211.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ハイヒールでダンスを踊ることはまずないからな",
      "startTime": 216.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、まずはハイヒールに慣れるところから\n始めたいと思います",
      "startTime": 223.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "ハイヒールを履いて頭に本を乗せ、落とさないように\n歩くことで、美しい姿勢で歩く技術を身につけます",
      "startTime": 229.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、凶器に使えそうなほど分厚い辞書を\n頭に乗せて歩いてみたいと思います",
      "startTime": 237.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
